OL,5,Cmental health
OL,7,FITV Granada's Tim Scott spoke to 12-
OL,8,Fyear-old Alfie Simcox about his latest
OL,9,Fcharity calendar
OL,11,FA young truck enthusiast is raising
OL,12,Fmoney towards helping lorry drivers'
OL,13,Fmental health, with a charity photo
OL,14,Fcalendar.
OL,16,F12-year-old Alfie Simcox, from Crewe,
OL,17,Fis a fixture at truck stops and
OL,18,Fmotorway bridges and well known among
OL,19,Fthe trucking community for his
OL,20,Fphotographs of their vehicles.
