OL,7,FFor several years, Alfie has produced
OL,8,Fa charity calendar and this year's
OL,9,Fwill raise funds towards the mental
OL,10,Fhealth charity MIND.
OL,12,FThe youngster chose to donate to them
OL,13,Fafter a friend, who was a driver, took
OL,14,Ftheir own life.
OL,16,FAlfie said: "Truck driving - you're
OL,17,Falone.
OL,19,F"If you go out on a Sunday night,
OL,20,Fyou're probably not going to be back
OL,21,Funtil Friday night.
