OL,7,F"It's lonely. People get really
OL,8,Fdepressed about it because they don't
OL,9,Fsee anyone."
OL,11,FTrucker Josh McLean, who lost the same
OL,12,Ffriend, added that the issue of
OL,13,Fdrivers' wellbeing needs to be
OL,14,Fdiscussed "100 per cent."
OL,16,F"Some drivers," he said, "can be away
OL,17,Ffrom their families for up to a month
OL,18,Fat a time.
OL,20,F"It's a lot of hours on your own."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
