OL,7,FAlfie has become a legend among long
OL,8,Fdistance drivers and his passion for
OL,9,Florries comes from having a family
OL,10,Ffilled with truckers.
OL,12,FHis mother, Stephanie, said: "He's got
OL,13,Fgrandads, uncles, cousins, his own dad
OL,14,F- all truck drivers.
OL,16,F"It's certainly running in his blood
OL,17,Fand it's something I know he's going
OL,18,Fto do."
