OL,7,FSo far, Alfie has raised nearly
OL,8,F#30,000 for good causes with his
OL,9,Fcalendars.
OL,11,FThis year's will be his last, though,
OL,12,Fas he is now selling his pictures
OL,13,Fdirectly to commercial transport
OL,14,Fcompanies.
OL,16,FBut all the money the youngster makes
OL,17,Fwill still go to charity.
